-- Togo Arrests Former Ivory Coast Defense Minister, RTI Says
-- B y   P a u l i n e   B a x
-- 2012-06-07T10:13:38Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-07/togo-arrests-former-ivory-coast-defense-minister-rti-says.html
Authorities in Togo arrested a former
Ivory Coast defense minister and handed him over to Ivorian
police, Radio Television Ivorienne reported.  A court in Abidjan issued an international arrest warrant
for Moise Lida Kouassi in June 2011, state-owned RTI said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Pauline Bax in Accra at 
 pbax@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
